text:
Prowess Pole is a wonderful place to start your passion for pole! 

-The new studio is spacious and clean;
-The instructor is fantastic, motivating, and helps you every step of the way; 
-There are performance opportunities in the studio if you wish to show off some of your skills to friends and the general audience!

It is a very welcoming and safe environment for those new to pole and are unsure of their abilities!! 5 stars ;)
